<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.828098>
    dc:description "FIGURE 33. Distribution of some sabellid species in South America. A) Perkinsiana antarctica (Kinberg, 1867), B) Perkinsiana assimilis (McIntosh, 1885), C) Pseudopotamilla platensis (Hartman, 1953) (circles) and P. knightjonesae sp. nov., (star denotes type locality)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/828098/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.828090>
    dc:description "FIGURE 29. Pseudopotamilla knightjonesae sp. nov. A) Branchial crown, dorsal view, B) radiolar eyes and collar, dorsal view, C) radiolar tip, D) branchial crown and collar, dorsal view. Arrows in A and B point to radiolar eyes. Scale bars: A, B 0. 6 mm, C 0.1 mm, D 0.6 mm. Abbreviation: apr anterior peristomial ring. Stain: A, B Shirla. Specimens: A, B, D paratypes, UANL 8112, C holotype, UANL 8111." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/828090/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.828088>
    dc:description "FIGURE 28. Pseudopotamilla knightjonesae sp. nov. A) Anterior thoracic segments and branchial crown, dorsal view, B) same, ventral view, C, D) same, lateral view. Scale bars: A, B 1.3 mm, C, D 0.6 mm. Abbreviations: apr anterior peristomial ring, df dorsal flange, vf ventral flange, vsc ventral shield of chaetiger 1. Stain: A – D Shirla. Specimens: A, B, D holotype, UANL 8111, C paratype, UANL 8112." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/828088/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.828092>
    dc:description "FIGURE 30. Pseudopotamilla knightjonesae sp. nov. A) Tubes, B) boring worms, C) posterior end, D) thoracic paleate notochaeta, E) abdominal elongate broadly hooded neurochaetae, F – H) thoracic companion chaetae and uncini, I) abdominal uncini. Scale bars: A 1.2 mm, B 2 mm, C 0.4 mm, D, E 20 µm, F – I 30 µm. Specimens: A – C paratypes, UANL 8112, D – I holotype, UANL 8111." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/828092/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

